<template>
  <ShopInfo :iten="item" />
</template>
<script>
import ShopInfo from '../../components/ShopInfo';
export default {
  name: "Shop",
  components: { ShopInfo },
  setup() {
    const item = {
      _id: "1",
      name: "沃尔玛",
      imgUrl: "http://www.dell-lee.com/imgs/vue3/near.png",
      sales: 10000,
      expressLimit: 0,
      expressPrice: 5,
      slogan: "VIP尊享满89元减4元运费券",
    }
    return{item}
  }
};
</script>
